code: var _this=this;import axios from'axios';export var register=function register(newUser){return axios.post('/signup',{username:newUser.username,masterkey:newUser.masterkey}).then(function(res){return res.data;}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};export var login=function login(user){return axios.post('/login',{username:user.username,masterkey:user.masterkey}).then(function(res){localStorage.setItem('token',res.data.token);localStorage.setItem('id',res.data.id);return res.data;}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};export var credentials=function credentials(newProgram){return axios.post('/add-program',{program:newProgram.program,username:newProgram.username,password:newProgram.password,id:newProgram.id}).then(function(res){return res.data;}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};export var programs=function programs(listPrograms){var token=localStorage.getItem('tok');if(!token){history.push('/');}return axios.get('/programs?token='+token,{program:programs.program,username:programs.username,password:programs.password}).then(function(res){console.log(res.data);return res.data;}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};export var remove=function remove(programName){return axios.post('/remove-program',{program:programName}).then(function(res){if(res.data.error){_this.props.history.push('/');}else{return res.data;}}).catch(function(err){console.log(err);});};
